## Benefits

1. **Enhanced Productivity**: Context-aware agent routing reduces manual agent switching
2. **Improved Safety**: Visual indicators and automated checks prevent rule violations
3. **Better Onboarding**: Clear agent mappings help new team members understand workflows
4. **Zero Breaking Changes**: All existing processes remain functional
5. **IDE Flexibility**: Team members can use their preferred IDE without workflow changes

## Maintenance

- Update AI_POLICY.md for core rule changes
- Update AI_POLICY_CURSOR.md for policy clarifications
- Update .cursorrules for workflow adjustments
- Update cursor_adapters.md for agent configuration changes
- All changes must maintain cross-IDE compatibility